  <name>Folder Buddies</name>
  <summary>Share and mount folders over encrypted peer-to-peer connections</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Folder Buddies lets you host a local folder and mount it on another
      computer as a native virtual filesystem. Connection metadata and file data
      are protected with short-code pairing and end-to-end encryption.
    </p>
  </description>
